<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en"
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
      xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
      xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
      lang="en"
      metal:use-macro="context/main_template/macros/master"
      i18n:domain="plone">
  <body>
    
    <metal:block 
       fill-slot="top_slot"
       tal:define="disable_column_one python:request.set('xdisable_plone.leftcolumn',1);
                   disable_column_two python:request.set('disable_plone.rightcolumn',1);" />
    
    <metal:main fill-slot="main">

      <h1 class="documentFirstHeading">Vote on the Plone Conference Talks</h1>
      <p>This year we have decided to open up the talk selection process to the wider community.
	Below is the list of proposed talks for the conference. Alas, we don't quite have enough
	room in the schedule to fit all of them, so we need your help in deciding which talks
	will be accepted. It will also help us schedule to talks to try and reduce the number of
        conflicts between very popular sessions.</p>
      <p>Please register your vote against the talks you wish to see at the conference. You
	can vote on as many talks as you wish. The order presented here is random. You can click
	on the talks type (eg. 'New to Plone') to just view talks of that type, and you can click
        on the name of the speaker to see their biography.</p>

      <p><em>The deadline for voting on the talks is Friday, 17th September. Speakers will be notified by Monday, 21st September.</em></p>

      <div class="filter" tal:condition="request/keyword|nothing">
	<span>Talk filter: <span tal:omit-tag="" tal:content="request/keyword"></span>
        <a tal:attributes="href request/URL0">View all talks</a></span>
      </div>

      <div class="talk" tal:repeat="talk view/talks">
      <a tal:attributes="name talk/getId"></a>
      <tal:block tal:define="talkview talk/@@talk">

       <h3 tal:content="talk/title">talk title</h3>
       <div class="byline"><p class="discreet">

         <p><span class="discreet"><a href="#" tal:attributes="onclick string:$('#bio-${talkview/getCSSId}').show();; return false;;">
         <span tal:replace="talk/name"/>, 
	 <tal:block tal:condition="talk/company">
         <span tal:replace="talk/company"/>,
         </tal:block>
         <span tal:replace="talk/country"/>
          </a></span></p>


       <div class="bio" tal:attributes="id string:bio-${talkview/getCSSId}">
           <p tal:content="structure talkview/bio">Speaker Bio</p>
       </div>


         <p class="discreet">
	 <tal:block tal:repeat="keyword talkview/keywords">
	   <a tal:attributes="href string:${request/URL0}?keyword=${keyword}"
              tal:content="keyword">keyword</a><span tal:omit-tag="" tal:condition="not:repeat/keyword/end">,</span>
	 </tal:block>
         </p>


       </div>
       <div class="vote" tal:attributes="id string:vote-${talkview/getCSSId}">
       <tal:block tal:condition="not:talkview/selected">
         <a href="#" tal:attributes="onclick string:$.ajax({ type: 'POST', url: '${talk/absolute_url}/@@addvote', data: '', dataType: 'html', success: function(html){ $('#vote-${talkview/getCSSId}').html('<div><img src=\'/++resource++netsight.ploneconf2010_theme.images/star.png\' height=\'80\' width=\'60\' alt=\'thanks\' /></div>')}});; return false;">
         <img src="/++resource++netsight.ploneconf2010_theme.images/thumbs-up.png" 
              height="80" width="60" 
              tal:attributes="alt string:Vote for this talk: ${talk/title}" />
         </a>
       </tal:block>
       <tal:block tal:condition="talkview/selected">
          <img src="/++resource++netsight.ploneconf2010_theme.images/star.png" height="80" width="60" alt="thanks" />
       </tal:block>
         <br />

<span tal:condition="not:context/@@plone_portal_state/anonymous"
      tal:content="talkview/score" />

       </div>
       <div class="synopsis">
           <p tal:content="structure talkview/description">Talk description</p>
       </div>

       <div style="clear:both"></div>

       <div class="control" tal:attributes="id string:control-${talkview/getCSSId}">
          <span class="discreet"><a href="#" tal:attributes="onclick string:$('#detail-${talkview/getCSSId}').show();; $('#control-${talkview/getCSSId}').hide();; return false;;">View speakers submission notes</a></span>
       </div>
       <div class="detail" tal:attributes="id string:detail-${talkview/getCSSId}">
           <p tal:content="structure talkview/detail">Talk detail</p>
       </div>


      </tal:block>       
      </div>

    </metal:main>

  </body>
</html>
